               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; several group of lines on the incipit page, alternating with black lines; incipit of sections, elements of the punctuation signs, elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Text I-1 includes the hymns:</note>
                     <note>- ʾO-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst dǝngǝl bä-kǝlʾe Maryam wäladitä ʾamlak ... "O my Lady, Holy Two-fold Virgin Mary, Godbearing ..."(fols. 7vb-8ra)</note>
                     <note>- Sälam läki ʾo-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä Maryam ʾǝmmu lä bǝrhan wä-ʾǝmmä mädḫǝn ... "Salutation to you, o my Lady Mary, Mother of the Light and Mother of the Saviour ..." (fol. 8ra-rb).</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>The miracles (Text I-4) are not numbered.</note>
                  </msItem>
